trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"> </xref> 및 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"> </xref> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A> method, and it indicates that the connection process has begun (for example, a user has selected a control and clicked a connect verb), but is not yet completed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>이벤트에 의해 발생 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A>메서드를 연결 프로세스는 시작 되었음을 나타냅니다 (예를 들어 사용자가 컨트롤을 선택 하 고 연결 동사를 클릭), 아직 완료 되지.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>

trans-unit.source: The event provides an opportunity to cancel a connection before it is complete.
trans-unit.target: 이벤트 완료 되기 전에 연결을 취소할 수를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the connection is successfully completed, this event is followed by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event.
trans-unit.target: 연결이 성공적으로 완료 되 면이 이벤트가 다음는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A> method, and it indicates that a user has clicked a disconnect verb, or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A> method has otherwise been called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>이벤트에 의해 발생 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A>메서드를 사용자가 연결 끊기 동사를 클릭 했음을 나타냅니다 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A>메서드를 호출 했음을.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>

trans-unit.source: The event provides an opportunity to cancel the process of ending a connection before it is complete.
trans-unit.target: 이벤트 완료 되기 전에 연결을 종료 하는 과정을 취소할 수를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the connection is ended successfully, this event is followed by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event.
trans-unit.target: 연결이 성공적으로 종료 되 면이 이벤트가 다음는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs class contains information about the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> events.
trans-unit.target: WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs 클래스에 대 한 정보는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>및 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>이벤트.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>

trans-unit.source: It provides access to the Web Parts controls that are being connected or disconnected.
trans-unit.target: 제공 되는 웹 파트 컨트롤에 대 한 액세스 연결 또는 연결 끊김.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs"></xref> class without a specified connection.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs"> </xref> 지정된 된 연결 없이 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control providing data in the connection.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 컨트롤 연결에서 데이터를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The connection point for providing data.
trans-unit.target: 데이터를 제공 하는 데 연결 지점입니다.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control consuming data in the connection.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 연결에서 데이터를 사용을 제어합니다.

trans-unit.source: The connection point for consuming data.
trans-unit.target: 데이터를 사용 하기 위한 연결 지점입니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs"></xref> class with the specified connection.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs"> </xref> 클래스 지정한 연결을 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control providing data in the connection.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 컨트롤 연결에서 데이터를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The connection point for providing data.
trans-unit.target: 데이터를 제공 하는 데 연결 지점입니다.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts control consuming data in the connection.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 연결에서 데이터를 사용을 제어합니다.

trans-unit.source: The connection point for consuming data.
trans-unit.target: 데이터를 사용 하기 위한 연결 지점입니다.

trans-unit.source: The Web Parts connection involved in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: 연결에 관련 웹 파트는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"> </xref> 또는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"> </xref> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the Web Parts connection involved in the event.
trans-unit.target: 이벤트와 관련 된 웹 파트 연결을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> involved in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> involved in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"></xref> event.

trans-unit.source: Gets the Web Parts control acting as the consumer in the connection.
trans-unit.target: 연결에 소비자 역할을 하는 웹 파트 컨트롤을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> acting as the consumer in the connection.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> 연결에 소비자 역할을 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the connection point that consumes data in the Web Parts connection.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 연결에서 데이터를 사용 하는 연결 지점을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConsumerConnectionPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConsumerConnectionPoint"></xref>.

trans-unit.target: 연결에서 공급자 역할을 하는 웹 파트 컨트롤을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> acting as the provider in the connection.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> 연결에서 공급자 역할을 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the connection point that provides data in the Web Parts connection.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 연결에서 데이터를 제공 하는 연결 지점을 가져옵니다.
